                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-777-18620707 t18620707-777-punishment-54"></join>Confined Eighteen Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">ADJOURNED TO MONDAY, AUGUST</hi> 18, 1862.</p>
